{
  "name": "AddIn",
  "summary": "<p><strong>AddIn</strong> 对象是 <strong>AddIns</strong> 集合的成员。<strong>AddIns</strong> 集合包含 ET 所有可用加载宏的列表（不论这些加载宏是否已安装）。此列表与 <strong>“加载宏”</strong> 对话框中显示的加载宏列表对应。</p>\n<p>使用 <strong>AddIns</strong>(<em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em> 是加载宏标题或索引号）可返回单个 <strong>AddIn</strong> 对象。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例安装“ANALYS32”加载宏。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ANALYS32&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Installed</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>请勿混淆加载宏标题（出现在 <strong>“加载宏”</strong> 对话框中）与加载宏名称（加载宏的文件名）。必须严格按照 <strong>“加载宏”</strong> 对话框中的标题书写加载宏标题，但不必匹配大小写。</p>\n<p>加载宏索引号代表加载宏在 <strong>“加载宏”</strong> 对话框内 <strong>“可用加载宏”</strong> 框中的位置。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例创建一个列表，包含可用加载宏的指定属性。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> sheet = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>)\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Rows</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Font</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Bold</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1:D1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = [<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Name&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Full Name&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Title&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Installed&quot;</span>]\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Cells</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n        sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Cells</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FullName</span>\n        sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Cells</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Title</span>\n        sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Cells</span>(i + <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Installed</span>\n    }\n    sheet.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CurrentRegion</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Columns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AutoFit</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong>Add</strong> 方法将加载宏添加到可用加载宏列表中，但不安装加载宏。将加载宏的 <strong>Installed</strong> 属性设为 <strong>True</strong> 可安装加载宏。要安装可用加载宏列表中没有的加载宏，必须先使用 <strong>Add</strong> 方法，然后设置 <strong>Installed</strong> 属性。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例添加并安装未显示的加载项。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> addin = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;D:\\\\ANALYS32.XLL&quot;</span>)\n    addin.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Installed</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>使用 <strong>Workbooks</strong>(<em>index</em>)（其中 <em>index</em> 是加载宏文件名而非标题）可返回对与某一加载宏相对应的工作簿的引用。因为加载宏通常不出现在 <strong>Workbooks</strong> 集合中，所以必须使用其文件名来指定。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 ANALYS32 加载宏的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> addin = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ANALYS32&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`加载项的名称：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${addin.Name}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 ANALYS32 加载宏的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ANALYS32&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>如果 <strong>Installed</strong> 属性为 <strong>True</strong>，但调用加载宏中的函数仍旧失败，那么可能并未真正地加载了该加载宏。这是因为 <strong>Addin</strong> 对象代表了加载宏的存在及安装状态，但并不代表加载宏工作簿中的实际内容。为保证已安装的加载宏被加载，应当打开该加载宏工作簿。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例打开第一个加载宏的工作簿。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-comment\">// the add-in workbook isn&#x27;t currently open. Manually open it.</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Workbooks</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Open</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FullName</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>代表单个加载宏，不论该加载宏是否已加载。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong> 对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个代表指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示一条有关创建 myObject 的应用程序的消息。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)\n{\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>) {\n      <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n  }\n  <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n      <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n  }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "CLSID",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个只读的唯一标识符，或识别对象的 CLSID。<strong>String</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一个加载宏的唯一标识符赋值给A1单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CLSID</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第二个加载宏的唯一标识符。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">CLSID</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Creator",
      "summary": "<p>如果该对象是在 ET 中创建的，则此属性返回字符串 XCEL，它等同于十六进制的数字 5843454C。<strong>Creator</strong> 属性是为 Macintosh 上的 ET 设计的，在 Macintosh 上，每个应用程序都具有一个四字符的创建者代码。例如，ET 的创建者代码为 XCEL。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 32 位整数，该整数指示在其中创建此对象的应用程序。只读 <strong>Long</strong> 类型。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "XlCreator",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "FullName",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回对象的名称（以字符串表示），包括其磁盘路径。<strong>String</strong> 型，只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示每一个可用加载宏的路径及文件名。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">for</span> (<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> i = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>; i &lt;= <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>; i++) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(i).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FullName</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例将第一个加载宏的路径及文件名赋值给A1单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">FullName</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Installed",
      "summary": "<p>将此属性设为 <strong>True</strong> 将安装指定加载宏，并调用 Auto_Add 函数。将此属性设为 <strong>False</strong> 则移去指定加载宏，并调用 Auto_Remove 函数。</p>\n",
      "description": "<p>如果安装了此加载宏，则该属性值为 <strong>True</strong>。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 ANALYS32 加载宏的安装状态。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> addIn = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ANALYS32&quot;</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (addIn.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Installed</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The ANALYS32 add-in is installed&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;The ANALYS32 add-in is not installed&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例安装第一个加载宏。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Installed</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": false
    },
    {
      "name": "IsOpen",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果加载项当前打开，则返回 <strong>True</strong>。只读 <strong>Boolean</strong> 类型</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 ANALYS32 加载宏是否处于打开状态。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ANALYS32&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsOpen</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例判断第一个加载宏是否处于打开状态，并通知用户。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">IsOpen</span>) {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;加载项当前处于打开状态&quot;</span>)\n    } <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span> {\n        <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;加载项当前处于关闭状态&quot;</span>)\n    }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "boolean",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Name",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，它代表对象的名称。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例将第一个加载宏的名称赋值给B1单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> addin = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;B1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = addin.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示第二个加载宏的名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> addin = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">AddIns</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">`加载宏的名称：<span class=\"hljs-subst\">${addin.Name}</span>`</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "string",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Parent",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回指定对象的父对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "",
      "type": "Object",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Path",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>String</strong> 值，它代表应用程序的完整路径，不包括末尾的分隔符和应用程序名称。</p>\n",
